{"title":"献给亚澳工会会议代表们","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给亚澳工会会议代表们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年十一月十六夜，周恩来总理公宴亚澳工会会议代表们。伊朗代表ＡＬＩ　ＭＡＨＭＥＤ和我谈得很好，把两人谈到的和没有谈到的。写一首诗，献给代表们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才发见了世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界怎么会存在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不会象今天的伟大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我兴奋了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见着世界劳工代表们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见着世界的主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见着世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才认识了人类。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的生存，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠它的文明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文明的表现和传授，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠它的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有见到手的劳动的代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里是人类啊？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只算没有见到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的中华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是由工人阶级领导的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是以工农联盟为基础。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这中间分析起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是农，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调合起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇向中华国土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断地浇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开花了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么花？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中华人民民主。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三国的代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从莫斯科来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到了中华人民的首都！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京之郊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们代表着什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表着生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表着文明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表着民主和平和康乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们的幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的辛劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如何是好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要大家来享受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要大家不怕辛劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"享受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人们辛劳以后应得的酬报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人们在天职上应有的报效。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是脑力劳动者中间的一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经这样想过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一群人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右一群人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么老是他欺侮着你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你压迫着我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么不把几十个国家溶化起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围成了一个？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各说各的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各写各的文字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化上相互地封锁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依我想来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各民族间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有它的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但该有一种世界共通的语言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有它的文字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但该有一种世界共通的文字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有意思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充分地表达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才不会错误，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此天下一家呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少一个不觉少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多一个也不嫌多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有待于大家努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们该负起责任来这样做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们唱个歌儿罢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要唱最雄壮的格调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最调和的音波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是那一国的国歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是全世界人类之歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}